  canonical="/hesco-bill/"
  introContent={`
    <p>Hyderabad Electric Supply Company (HESCO) supplies electricity to over 2.1 million consumers across eight districts of lower and central Sindh: <strong>Hyderabad</strong>, <strong>Mirpurkhas</strong>, <strong>Tharparkar</strong>, <strong>Badin</strong>, <strong>Thatta</strong>, <strong>Shaheed Benazirabad (Nawabshah)</strong>, <strong>Sanghar</strong>, and <strong>Matiari</strong>. Established in 1998, HESCO covers Pakistan's second-largest province's southern half — an area of immense agricultural and cultural significance.</p>
    <p><strong>Hyderabad city</strong> — Pakistan's eighth-largest city — serves as HESCO's operational hub. Once the capital of Sindh under the Talpur Mirs and a major commercial centre, Hyderabad remains an important industrial city with a significant population of urban consumers. Beyond the city, HESCO covers <strong>Tharparkar</strong> (Pakistan's only Hindu-majority district and one of the world's largest coal reserves), <strong>Badin</strong> (coastal Sindh), <strong>Thatta</strong> (home to the UNESCO-listed Makli necropolis), and the rice-belt districts of Mirpurkhas and Nawabshah.</p>
    <p>HESCO should not be confused with SEPCO — a common source of confusion for Sindh consumers. <strong>HESCO covers lower and central Sindh</strong> while <strong>SEPCO covers upper Sindh</strong> (Sukkur, Larkana, Khairpur). If you live in Sukkur or Larkana, check the <a href="/sepco-bill/">SEPCO bill page</a>. If you live in Hyderabad, Mirpurkhas, Nawabshah, or Thatta, you are an HESCO consumer.</p>
    <p>To check your HESCO bill online, enter your <strong>14-digit HESCO reference number</strong> in the bill checker above. HESCO uses the same PITC server as all other WAPDA DISCOs. Your reference number is printed at the top of every HESCO electricity bill.</p>
  
    <p>PakistanBill.online is <strong>Pakistan's only platform</strong> covering all 19 utility providers. Alongside HESCO, also check: <a href="/sepco-bill/">SEPCO bill</a> for Sukkur | <a href="/k-electric-bill/">K-Electric bill</a> for Karachi | <a href="/qesco-bill/">QESCO bill</a> for Balochistan | <a href="/ssgc-bill/">SSGC gas bill</a>. Use our <a href="/electricity-bill-calculator/">electricity bill calculator</a>, visit our <a href="/dashboard/">bill dashboard</a>, or read <a href="/blog/how-to-pay-online/">how to pay bills online</a>. See our complete <a href="/hyderabad/">Hyderabad utility bills guide</a>.</p>
  `}
  howToSteps={[
    "Find your 14-digit HESCO reference number — printed in bold at the top of your HESCO electricity bill.",
